Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nwill make tonight sparkle, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:11.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you enjoy my somewhat troublesome \Nrival and a black miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two steel crows in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three more on their other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! They've even prepared armored cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kudos to the Metro Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please reconsider, Young Master Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about tonight's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:37.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you got backed into a corner like \Nlast time and something happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,no apology of mine would suffice for the \Nghost of Toichi-sama, the previous Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:48.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. You're always like this \Nbefore a big job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:50.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, tonight I'm not the son of \Nillusionist Kuroba Toichi, your former boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:59.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,nor am I high school student \NYoung Master Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:01.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm the guy \Nwho's got everyone talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the flashy scoundrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you mention it, \Nthat was a close call, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.99,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too easy! Like \Ntaking candy from a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.20,Signs - readability,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief Appears Yet Again \Nand Steals the Treasure with Style!\N\NKid the Phantom Thief Dazzles Police Again\N with His Daring Crime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a cinch, I could pull off the \Nnext job with both hands tied behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Number of Kid's female fans skyrocketing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky's the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:15.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Female fans skyrocketing," my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is no fan of that thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:23.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, when it comes to the scummiest \Nof scumbags, he's at the head of the pack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't let it get to you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:30.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame Kid if he gives that \Nthird-rate inspector father of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,a spanking every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's... One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Great Thief Who Can't Be Caught!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.24,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Thief Who Can't Be Caught!\N\NIn-depth analysis of the mysterious \NKid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:45.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He always either throws away what he \Nsteals or secretly returns it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a criminal thrill-seeker \Npretending to be a good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:51.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what I like about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute, like a mischievous boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him put one over on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you slice it, \Nhe's a criminal! A bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you saw Kid's next target \Non the news, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You mean the old clock tower \Nin front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That belongs \Nto everyone in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.18,Signs - readability,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs22}Kid the Phantom Thief's Next Target, \Nthe Clock Tower, Slated for Relocation\N\NMetro Police Enact Strict Security Measures,\N Seal Off Entrance\N\N"I Hope They Protect the Clock Tower," \NSays Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you think it's terrible \Nthat he means to steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...that clock tower is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard they're gonna \Nmove the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:31.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it the symbol of \Nsome amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:36.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's saying that as long as it's \Ngoing away, Kid might as well steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I don't know what you're up to, \Nbut I would call off this job if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:49.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, I'm not Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:55.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"When the bells of the old clock tower \Nring out for the 20,000th time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:58.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the magus of light will \Ncome flying from the east
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to destroy the sinner in white."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that crap supposed to be my fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a fortune. It's a prophecy \NLucifer the Devil shared with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luci...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That clock will strike for the 20,000th time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,on the night you announced for the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not you believe it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This goes for the choppers in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the squad cars \Naround the clock tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:35.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Report to me the moment you \Nsee any suspicious characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:41.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the guards in each block of the tower, \Nnobody gets past you without my say-so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think Kid will \Nshow up, Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:52.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"On Saturday, night of the full moon, \NI shall appear at the stroke of midnight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:56.79,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}On Saturday, night of the full moon, \NI shall appear at the stroke of midnight \Nto steal the towering clock\N right from under your nose. \N\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to steal the towering clock \Nright from under your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:01.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd need a crane or something \Nto swipe that huge clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he says he's gonna steal somethin', \Nhe's gonna steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the hand of the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,50 years ago, my father, the mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:17.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,spent a fortune to have the hands crafted \Nby a famous clockmaker overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Several large diamonds are \Ninlaid in the hour hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which makes it a valuable piece of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine he's after those jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the owner doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He insisted on checking out \Nthe security measures himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect it from the clutches of the thief \Nwho sent me his prankster advance notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,saying he would take my beloved clock tower, \Nwhich I inherited when my father passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. You can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,28 minutes and 30 seconds 'til it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Officer Sensui Yoichi \Nfrom Ekoda, 27 and single,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow your name and face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:11.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! How is it inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. An ant couldn't get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:24.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The amusement park side is saying if \Ndismantling it doesn't start tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it won't be ready by their opening day,\N so they'll cancel the purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Kid steals the gems from the \Nhour hand and realizes the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Right now, only you and I know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:40.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that I sold off the diamonds \Nand replaced them with fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kid targeting the clock, its value has \Nshot up, making now the best time to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out the gems aren't real after \Nthe tower's moved, it's not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the replicas are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a great, elusive thief \Ncouldn't steal that huge clock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,right in front of all these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay home, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:09.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoko, you're the only one \Ncheering against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Keiko, have you seen Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going to watch \Na magic show on TV tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:25.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I {\i1}am{\i0} the only one who remembers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You were out on patrol when you saw \Na suspicious guy who looked like Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:37.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! He dropped this weird hat and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's Kid's silk hat and cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the front entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our own has found \NKid the Phantom Thief's hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That helicopter's definitely the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:02.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He gives off strong, clear energy, \Njust like Kuroba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He also has the cunning of a demon and keen \Neyes that can penetrate a person's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's goin' on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see an extra helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently reinforcements from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask for additional help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the one who found Kid's silk hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be safe, please show me \Nyour badge and license.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me your name, age, and birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sensui Yoichi, 27 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My birthday's on June 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori is eagerly \Nawaiting you on the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Just in case, \Ntell me your license number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:51.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 6286-0552-4810.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kid the Phantom Thief! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You found Kid in the building?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Currently, teams \NC and D are in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure it's the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After asking his name, age, and birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I requested his license number as \Nadvised, and got him red-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,License number?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:27.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. That thief is a master of disguise,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so the idea is, it's likely he can remember \Ndetails the average person can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the boy sent \Nfrom HQ as backup said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Boy," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat! Please seal off all entrances \Nand exits to the clock tower immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And keep them sealed until I give the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:48.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, he's like a rat in a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nakamura and Kawata from team D!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:54.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost sight of the target \Nnear the third-floor restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably still very close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ventilation opening in the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the cover been unscrewed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:16.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue your pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! The inspector's \Nreally sharp tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless someone's giving the inspector advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Megure! I figured it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the idea of bringing a kid here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're in different divisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. I promised him \Na ride in the helicopter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:47.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and since we were airborne anyway, \Nwe flew over to the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:52.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Pardon me, \Nbut we don't have time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to catch that thief,\N follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His identity has been exposed before \Ncommitting the crime, so he's agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His plan is starting to go off track.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best chance to arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:26.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kudo Shinichi, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a high school detective who's solved \None mysterious murder case after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're in a different division, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with a phantom thief here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:42.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, a high school student \Nisn't in any division...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The point is, this is the job of the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a civilian, you'd better just \Nsit quietly in that chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid's been spotted in a ventilation \Nshaft, disguised as a cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:55.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nakamura! It seems the target means \Nto exit from another ventilation opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The prey is as good as in your claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me your current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:12.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, I'm not sure, since I've \Nbeen crawling around in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We went up one floor, so I can tell you \Nwe're on the 4th floor, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries. All 28 ventilation openings \Nin the building are now secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:26.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue support. He's out of places to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Officers guarding the ventilation openings \Non the 4th floor, prepare to make an arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again, giving orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost sight of the target \Nat a ventilation shaft exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your current location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The east hallway on the 4th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:48.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The target shed his police officer disguise \Nand is currently escaping down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requesting immediate backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-K-Kid the Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! He panicked and \Nditched his police disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:03.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All officers on the third and fourth \Nfloors, proceed to the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But how does that boy know so much about \Nthe structure of this clock tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A little while ago, I sent the data \Nwe have here over to his computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is crawling with police officers,\N so taking off his cop disguise
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:28.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is like a crab that discards its shell, \Nroaming around the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the time he noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Smoke is coming \Nout of the scaffolding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The clock's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're amazing, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid... Kid, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wobbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in God's green earth is goin' on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but can you get us a \Nlittle closer to the clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An officer suddenly came out \Nof the ventilation shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After nailing us with some weird spray,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,h-he went outside from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he should be clearly \Nvisible from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Nakamori! I found Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he's—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:04.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Inspector Nakamori, but I don't have time \Nto play games with you guys right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:10.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've got a sharp joker \Nin your hand this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:14.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're going to call someone \Nhere, please do so only after
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,cracking the code in the center \Nof the clock face here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Code?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock face is quivering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean, Kudo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He cut the light that was shining on \Nthe clock face during the smokescreen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then covered the face with a giant \Nscreen he'd prepared beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, he projected the image \Nof a clock face without hands
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:41.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,from a projector on the \Nconstruction scaffolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't a trick like that \Nbe figured out quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That trick is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's behind the screen right now, \Nremoving the gems from the hour hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow this for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who's shootin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:09.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! There's a helicopter this close?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to fly away \Nin my hang glider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:15.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, unlucky spirits \Nwandering through Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Obey the Crimson Covenant. Turn your \Nremains into flames and come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Displaying your power \Nin front of all these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Kuroba-kun will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Kudo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't hit anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not the issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the magic show finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:56.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a look at the man\N behind the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:15.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell right into the middle \Nof the crowd with that screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:19.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding him in the crowd will be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:21.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you shootin' at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:29.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Inspector, \Ndid he say something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A code?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.67,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{just katakana syllables, no sense translating}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:43.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure he etched those characters \Ninto the center of the clock face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's important evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:53.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to cancel the clock tower's \Nscheduled move until the code is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:53.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{same}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:57.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was gonna do anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it worked out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock tower is safe \Nand his crime was foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not quite, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He left a code on the face and entrusted \Nthe clock tower to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:15.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,taking it out of the hands of the owner,\N who intended to relocate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His encoded message is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.41,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{same; there, already translated}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:25.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the katakana to roman characters, \Nmove the vowels over one space clockwise, and:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:28.93,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{translated in last line already}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"This bell has lost its luster."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:32.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \NI haven't heard his name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the thief's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:52.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I just moved here today
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm supposed to meet my dad here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's so busy with work that he's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kuroba Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kuroba Kaito. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could forget, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your negativity brought it\N all back, Jii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock tower job \Nwhen I almost got nabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, \Nwhatever happened to that clock tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You moved, so you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So they did relocate it, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:46.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,3... 2... 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That ringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:21:00.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, the cops investigated, \Nfound out the diamonds were fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the city bought the clock\N for a cheap price.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm after a Big Jewel, the Suzuki \Nconglomerate's crown jewel, the Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:15.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, I won't try to stop you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but like Toichi-sama always said, \N"When you face the audience, it's a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never be overconfident \Nor underestimate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:29.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but see into their hearts, \Nfocus on every nerve in your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:34.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,exert your talent to the utmost, always \Nmaintaining a smile and elegance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"And at all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,remember your poker face."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:53.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's meet again under the \Nbeautiful ringing of the bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:33.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, "Never be overconfident \Nor underestimate them,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but even though it was just for an instant,\N old man Nakamori saw my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I obviously need more training!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:42.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this, even Aoko suspects me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:45.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To get through this pinch, I'll have \Nto sew together a time interval,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and perform a subtle yet bold magic trick!
